<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- صحيح مسلم، وهو أحاديث عن أقوال النبيّ وأفعاله كما رواها صحابته وجمعت تحت عنوان الجامع الصحيح، دلهي، الهند<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- Sahih Muslim, being traditions of the saying and doings of the Prophet Muhamad as narrated by his Companions and compiled under the title Al-Jami’-us-Sahih.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
